| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2316 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a87bb3f9-df37-5199-95e5-071eec781c70"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
